spec_data.Name: ctags-etags
spec_data.License: GPLv2+ and LGPLv2+ and Public Domain
spec_data.Description:
This package will generate tags in a format which GNU Emacs understand,
it's a alternativ implementation of the GNU etags program.
Note: some command line options is not compatible with GNU etags.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 05 Aug 2017 11:00:46 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Exuberant Ctags for emacs tag format
